OL,3,CThird of people say university degree
OL,4,Cnot worth it as student loan inquiry
OL,5,Copens
OL,7,FA record third of people now think a
OL,8,Funiversity degree isn't worth the time
OL,9,Fand money, it has emerged, as an
OL,10,Finquiry by MPs into the student loan
OL,11,Fsystem in England begins on Tuesday.
OL,13,FConfidence has slumped amid declining
OL,14,Fjob prospects and anger over debt, a
OL,15,Fmajor survey of public opinion found.
OL,17,FBritish Social Attitudes researchers
OL,18,Fhave tracked attitudes on key issues
OL,19,Ffor over 20 years.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1780416668
OL,3,CThird of people say university degree
OL,4,Cnot worth it as student loan inquiry
OL,5,Copens
OL,7,FThe number saying it is not worth
OL,8,Fgoing to university hit a high of 34
OL,9,Fper cent last year, more than the 15
OL,10,Fper cent who said the same thing in
OL,11,F2005.
OL,13,FMeanwhile, the belief that graduates
OL,14,Fare better off in the long run has
OL,15,Fcollapsed from 50 per cent to 36 per
OL,16,Fcent over the same period.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1780416668
OL,3,CThird of people say university degree
OL,4,Cnot worth it as student loan inquiry
OL,5,Copens
OL,7,FThe findings of the BSA come amid
OL,8,Fpressure to reform the student loan
OL,9,Fsystem, with recent graduates
OL,10,Fdescribing it as unfair due to high
OL,11,Finterest rates and the unlikelihood of
OL,12,Fpaying off the debt.
OL,14,FMPs on the Treasury Select Committee
OL,15,Fare hearing from student organisations
OL,16,Fand experts on Tuesday, looking at all
OL,17,Fstudent loan plans in England and
OL,18,Fwhether repayment terms are
OL,19,F"reasonable".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1780416668
OL,3,CThird of people say university degree
OL,4,Cnot worth it as student loan inquiry
OL,5,Copens
OL,7,FLast month, the Treasury Committee
OL,8,Fpublished a summary of the results of
OL,9,Fits own public survey on student loans
OL,10,Fand the taxation of graduates.
OL,12,FIt had received more than 52,000
OL,13,Fresponses, one of the highest response
OL,14,Frates to a select committee inquiry
OL,15,Fever recorded.
OL,17,FThe inquiry was launched after
OL,18,Fcontroversy over Plan 2 loans, issued
OL,19,Fin England between September 2012 and
OL,20,FJuly 2023 and still being issued in
OL,21,FWales.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
