PN,31305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1780416668
OL,3,CThird of people say university degree
OL,4,Cnot worth it as student loan inquiry
OL,5,Copens
OL,7,FGraduates in England on plan 2 loans
OL,8,Frepay nine per cent of whatever they
OL,9,Fearn over a threshold, which is due to
OL,10,Fbe frozen at #29,385 from April 2027
OL,11,Ffor three years. The result is that
OL,12,Fmore will start repaying earlier.
OL,14,FMany students say they did not
OL,15,Funderstand the terms when they signed
OL,16,Fup.
OL,18,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,19,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,20,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,21,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
