OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1780416668
OL,3,CThird of people say university degree
OL,4,Cnot worth it as student loan inquiry
OL,5,Copens
OL,7,FGraduates in England are finishing
OL,8,Fdegrees with government loans
OL,9,Faveraging #53,000, a jump of 10 per
OL,10,Fcent in a year, as they increase their
OL,11,Fborrowing to meet the rising cost of
OL,12,Fliving, according to the Student Loans
OL,13,FCompany.
OL,15,FAlex Scholes, a BSA co-author, warned
OL,16,Fthat declining confidence in
OL,17,Funiversities risked further
OL,18,Fexacerbating financial problems in the
OL,19,Fhigher education sector.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1780416668
OL,3,CThird of people say university degree
OL,4,Cnot worth it as student loan inquiry
OL,5,Copens
OL,7,FHe said: "Universities are not just
OL,8,Feducational institutions, they are
OL,9,Fengines of social mobility and
OL,10,Feconomic growth, and play a vital role
OL,11,Fin defining Britain's cultural role on
OL,12,Fthe world stage.
OL,14,F"They are also under immense financial
OL,15,Fpressure, and it appears recent
OL,16,Fdebates about the fairness of student
OL,17,Floan repayment systems and the role of
OL,18,FAI on the job market have filtered
OL,19,Fthrough to people's views about the
OL,20,Fvalue of a degree.
OL,26,@oD@JOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
