CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1780416668
OL,3,CThird of people say university degree
OL,4,Cnot worth it as student loan inquiry
OL,5,Copens
OL,7,F"If public confidence continues to
OL,8,Ffall, we risk seeing the financial
OL,9,Fsituation become even worse."
